description:
Lenalee Lee is a 17-year-old Exorcist from Hong Kong and member of the European Branch of the http://anidb.net/ch32498 [Black Order].
After a Level 4 Akuma attacks the HQ, and many people were injured or killed, her anti-Akuma weapon, The Dark Boots, changed from Equipment to Crystal-type weapon, taking the form of two blood-red anklets. These new boots are made up of Lenalee`s blood and will repair themselves as long as she has blood in her body.
Source: Wikipedia, edited.
name: Lenalee Lee
